.SH "Detailed Description"
.PP 
Represents a company, corporation, or in-game faction\&. 

The \fBCompany\fP class stores immutable identifiers that describe an entity’s identity and branding in the simulation or game world\&. Its instances can be linked to tiles, assets, or scores via references or pointers\&. 
